OL,3,C'Sadness' as shopkeepers of 40 years
OL,4,Cstruggle to find buyer for their store
OL,6,FA shop in Chard, which was in the town
OL,7,Ffor 42 years, has closed after its
OL,8,Fowners were unable to sell it as an
OL,9,Fongoing concern.
OL,11,FBarrons of Chard was a menswear store
OL,12,Fand the only shop in the town that
OL,13,Fsold local school uniforms. With its
OL,14,Fowners retiring, it was hoped the
OL,15,Fbusiness could continue under a new
OL,16,Fowner.
OL,18,FHowever, despite coming close to
OL,19,Fselling, a prospective buyer pulled
OL,20,Fout due to a lack of confidence.
