OL,3,C'Sadness' as shopkeepers of 40 years
OL,4,Cstruggle to find buyer for their store
OL,6,FJohn and Mandy Barron say that
OL,7,Fillustrates just how hard it is in
OL,8,Fretail at the moment, with many
OL,9,Findependent businesses being forced to
OL,10,Fclose because of how poor trading
OL,11,Fconditions are.
OL,13,FMandy said: "It's very sad to see it
OL,14,Fempty. It would be much nicer to be
OL,15,Fleaving it with a new business coming
OL,16,Fin. It's sad to think of another empty
OL,17,Fshop.
