OL,6,FThankfully for Chard, some people
OL,7,Faren't taking that advice and are
OL,8,Fgiving it a go.
OL,10,FPeter John took on Chard Craft
OL,11,FButchers recently and said: "On a day-
OL,12,Fto-day we're doing ok at the moment.
OL,14,F"There seems to be more people out in
OL,15,Fthe town - Friday and Saturday we're
OL,16,Fseeing a lot more people out. It
OL,17,Fdefinitely needs more people like me -
OL,18,Fjust people who are looking to invest
OL,19,Fin the town."
