OL,4,Cstruggle to find buyer for their store
OL,6,FChard Town Council said: "The
OL,7,Fcommunity shops differently now to
OL,8,Fwhat they did 10 years ago. What is
OL,9,Fvitally important to Chard and it's
OL,10,FTown Council is ensuring the town has
OL,11,Fa solid infrastructure to support its
OL,12,Fcommunity and this has to be the
OL,13,Fpriority of every town in Somerset."
